snippet.title: Multishot OFFICIAL Trailer - 2D Multiplayer Platformer Game / steam
snippet.description:
Multishot is a 2D Multiplayer Shooter Platformer Game. customize your character, change your cosmetic and fight! Take the top of the leaderboard!

Join a match or start a server. You can play with up to 9 players .
